data.description: For half a century, PAT has aided the progress of North American manufacturing by supplying top-tier pigments, chemicals, plastics, and ingredients to industry leaders. We are proud to be your trusted partner in formulating success.

data.name: IncaTara Peruvian Tara Gum Powder
data.description: IncaTara Peruvian Tara Gum Powder is obtained by grinding the endosperm of the seeds of Caesalpinia spinosa (Fam. Leguminosae). It mainly consists of polysaccharides with high molecular weight, primarily composed of galactomannans. The main component is a linear chain of (1, 4)-beta-D-mannopyranose units, with alpha-D-galactopyranose units attached by (1-6) linkages. The ratio of mannose to galactose in tara gum is 3:1.

data.name: P.A.T. Products LCS 1171
data.description: P.A.T. Products LCS 1171 is a polyester-based TPU allowing for fast cycle times and ease of demoulding of the final item. This makes this product particularly indicated for injection moulding e.g. of footwear features and technical items.

data.name: P.A.T. Products LCS 1155
data.description: P.A.T. Products LCS 1155 is a polyester-based TPU specifically developed for extrusion of films and sheets. Characterized by very good mechanical properties and good melting behaviour, it exhibits an excellent processability and it is consequently suggested for the manufacturing of profiles, sheets, films and coating applications.

data.name: Laripur 7060
data.description: Laripur 7060 is a PTMG polyether-based TPU exhibiting very good hydrolytic stability and good microbial resistance. The standard version is designed for injection moulding e.g. of technical items while the extrusion grade (EG) for the production of mild breathable film for roofing.

data.name: P.A.T. Products Ketoblend
data.description: P.A.T. Products Ketoblend is rich in total fat, low in available carbohydrates, ideal to be formulated into powdered foods for ketogenic diets. It is also water soluble.

data.name: Laripur 7060 EG

data.name: P.A.T.
data.seo_description: Knowde is the first marketplace for chemicals, polymers and ingredients. Our leading-edge digital capabilities connect thousands of sellers and buyers every day.

data.name: Lemon #1 Flake Shellac
data.description: P.A.T Lemon #1 Flake Shellac is a resin produced by the female lac bug on trees in the forests of India and Thailand. Lemon #1 shellac, containing 2-5% natural shellac wax, yields milky dispersions of medium color shade in various solvents. Coatings and films of wax containing shellacs result in surfaces with a satin gloss.

data.name: Benzotriazole
data.description: Benzotriazole is a heterocyclic compound containing three nitrogen atoms with the chemical formula C7H6N2. Benzotriazole is known primarily as an effective corrosion inhibitor for copper and its alloys. The appearance is white or slightly yellow with fine granules.

data.name: Tolyltriazole
data.description: P.A.T Tolyltriazole is a heterocyclic compound containing three nitrogen atoms with the chemical formula C7H6N2. It is versatile and especially useful in systems where fluids are in continuous contact with metals that require protection. It can protect metals such as copper, zinc, cobalt, silver, aluminum, and steel when used in multi-metal systems with other corrosion inhibitors.

data.name: TEC-250 - Alkyl Phenolic Tackifier Resin
data.description: P.A.T TEC-250 - Alkyl Phenolic Tackifier Resin is a tackifier resin derived from the reaction between octyl phenol and formaldehyde. It is soluble in oils and compatible with various synthetic rubbers. The resin is in regular reddish pieces approximately 6 mm in length. Its primary application is as a tackifier in the tire and belt industry.

data.name: Gum Arabic #2 (Premium Kibbled)

summary.name: Synonyms
items: Acacia ampliceps gum, Acacia dealbata gum, Acacia fragilis gum, Acacia gum, Acacia leptopetala gum, Acacia ligulata gum, Acacia meisneri gum, Acacia pruinocarpa gum, Acacia salicina gum, Acacia senegal gum, Acacia syrup, Acacia victoriae gum, E 414, Gum acacia, Gum ovaline, Gum senegal, Gum thala, Gundar gum, Indian gum, Khair gum, Kordofan gum, Maklai gum, Ticacia Gum, Wattle gum

data.description: P.A.T Gum Arabic #2 (Premium Kibbled) is a dried exudate obtained from the stems and branches of Acacia seyal trees. Gum Arabic #2 is also known as gum talha or gum friable. The material is a mix of fragmented pieces with some whole tears present.

data.name: H-Tempo
data.description: P.A.T H-Tempo (also referred to as 4-Hydroxy-TEMPO) is used as a stabilizer for countering oxidation and/or the polymerization of unsaturated compounds such as acrylic acid, butadiene, styrene, etc. H-TEMPO is also used as a shortstopper for radical polymerization processes, e. g. in the manufacture of oligoester acrylates.

data.name: 1173 Photoinitiator 2-Hydroxyl-2-methylpropiophenone

summary.name: Synonyms
items: 1-Hydroxy-1-methylethyl phenyl ketone, 1-Phenyl-2-hydroxy-2-methyl-1-propanone, 1-Phenyl-2-methyl-2-hydroxypropanone, 2-Benzoyl-2-hydroxypropane, 2-Benzoyl-2-propanol, 2-Hydroxy-2-benzoylpropane, 2-Hydroxy-2-methyl-1-phenyl-1-propanone, 2-Hydroxy-2-methyl-1-phenylpropan-1-one, 2-Hydroxy-2-methyl-1-phenylpropane-1-one, 2-Hydroxy-2-methyl-1-phenylpropanone, 2-Hydroxy-2-methyl-1-propiophenone, 2-Hydroxy-2-methyl-propylphenone, 2-Hydroxy-2-methylphenylpropanone, 2-Hydroxy-2-methylpropiophenone, 2-Hydroxy-2,2-dimethylacetophenone, 2-Hydroxy-methylphenylpropan-1-one, 2-Methyl-2-hydroxy-1-phenyl-1-propanone, 2-Methyl-3-phenyl-3-oxopropan-2-ol, 2,2-Dimethyl-2-hydroxyacetophenone, Hydroxy dimethyl acetophenone, NSC 401744, Î±-Hydroxy-Î±-methylpropiophenone, Î±-Hydroxy-Î±,Î±-dimethylacetophenone, Î±-Hydroxyisobutyrophenone, Î±,Î±-Dimethyl-Î±-hydroxyacetophenone

data.description: P.A.T 1173 Photoinitiator 2-Hydroxyl-2-methylpropiophenone is a versatile, highly efficient, liquid photoinitiator used to initiate the photo-polymerisation of chemically unsaturated prepolymers - e.g. acrylates-in combination with mono or multifunctional monomers. 1173 is especially recommended when UV coatings are required to exhibit only minimal yellowing even after prolonged exposure to sunlight.

data.name: 184 Photoinitiator 1-Hydroxycyclohexyl phenyl ketone

summary.name: Synonyms
items: (1-Hydroxycyclohexyl)phenylmethanone, 1-Benzoyl-1-hydroxycyclohexane, 1-Benzoylcyclohexanol, 1-Hydroxy-1-cyclohexyl phenyl ketone, 1-Hydroxycyclohexyl phenyl ketone, NSC 401908, Î±-Hydroxy-Î±-cyclohexyl phenyl ketone, Î±-Hydroxycyclohexyl phenyl ketone

data.description: P.A.T 184 Photoinitiator 1-Hydroxycyclohexyl phenyl ketone is a highly efficient non-yellowing photoinitiator which is used to initiate the photo-polymerisation of chemically unsaturated prepolymers - e.g. acrylates - in combination with mono or multifunctional vinyl monomers. 184 is especially recommended when UV coatings are required to exhibit only minimal yellowing even after prolonged exposure to sunlight.

data.name: 2 Mercaptoethanol
data.description: P.A.T 2 Mercaptoethanol, also known as Beta-Mercaptoethanol, is a versatile chemical with applications spanning various industries. Primarily utilized in the production of water-borne coatings for acrylic resins, it serves as a crucial component for formulating corrosion inhibitors and stabilizers. Its role extends to acting as a tin-type stabilizer, a chain transfer agent in polymerization processes, and a valuable component in anti-corrosion systems for oilfield applications. As a member of the alcohols chemical family, 2-Mercaptoethanol plays a multifaceted role, contributing to the effectiveness and performance of diverse products across different industrial applications.

data.name: Antistat 00313
data.description: P.A.T Antistat 00313 is a quaternary ammonium compound in dibenzoate plasticizer. It appears as a clear, yellowish liquid and is suitable for use in all PVC applications. This additive can be formulated with plastisol blends or in melt-compounded vinyl. Importantly, Antistat 00313 is an antistatic additive rather than a conductivity agent. Due to its cationic character and high polarity, the electrical resistance of systems containing Antistat 00313 is significantly reduced, even when used in small quantities.

data.name: Calcium Stearate

summary.name: Synonyms
items: Calcium bis(stearate), Calcium distearate, Calcium octadecanoate

data.description: P.A.T Calcium Stearate is a fine, white powder. It is an insoluble salt of calcium, stearic acid, and palmitic acid. Recognized as physiologically safe, calcium stearate has gained increasing importance in recent years. This substance remains insoluble in most solvents. While it dissolves only slightly when heated in aromatic compounds, chlorinated hydrocarbons, or vegetable and mineral oils and waxes,

data.name: Diammonium 2,2'-azinobis[3-ethyl-2,3-dihydrobenzothiazole-6-sulfonate]
data.description: P.A.T Diammonium 2,2'-azinobis[3-ethyl-2,3-dihydrobenzothiazole-6-sulfonate] is a cutting-edge product within the Base Chemicals and Intermediates category. Classified under the Intermediates and Other Intermediates within the Base Chemicals and Intermediates Product Families, this powdered substance exhibits a distinctive yellowish green to green hue. With its advanced chemical composition, P.A.T Diammonium serves as a crucial component in various industrial processes, contributing to the synthesis of diverse chemical intermediates. Its powdered physical form ensures ease of handling and integration into a wide range of applications within the realm of base chemicals and intermediates.

data.name: Glycine

summary.name: Synonyms
items: Aminoacetic Acid, Aminoethanoic Acid, Glycin, Glycocoll, Glycolixir, Glykokoll, Hgly

data.description: P.A.T Glycine is an amino acid characterized by having a single hydrogen atom as its side chain. It holds the distinction of being the simplest stable amino acid, featuring the chemical formula NHâCHâCOOH. In its physical state, glycine appears as a white powder.

data.name: Gum Damar
data.description: P.A.T Gum Damar is a natural gum damar resin obtained from shorea trees. P.A.T Gum Damar appears as white to yellowish-white translucent, globular to pear-shaped grains, irregular fragments, or stalactite masses. It is insoluble in water but soluble in toluene.

data.name: Gum Olibanum
data.description: P.A.T Gum Olibanum is an aromatic resin derived from trees and is commonly utilized in various applications such as incense, perfume, and aromatherapy. The resin is obtained through a process known as "tapping," which involves extracting the hardened sap from the trees. The quality of gum olibanum is assessed based on factors like color, aroma, size, and purity. Applications for gum olibanum are diverse and include incense, religious fumigation, flavors, and fragrances. It is a common ingredient in incense formulations, contributing to the aromatic profile of the incense, and is used in religious practices for fumigation purposes, adding a fragrant element to ceremonial rituals.

data.name: High Flow Flake Shellac
data.description: P.A.T High Flow Flake Shellac is a resin produced by the female lac bug on trees in the forests of India and Thailand. This specific type of shellac, known for its high flow characteristics, is particularly well-suited for abrasive and grinding wheel applications. Its unique properties make it a valuable choice in scenarios that involve abrasion and grinding. Additionally, high-flow shellac can be employed in various applications where standard (rangeeni) shellac is typically used, showcasing its versatility across different uses and industries.

data.name: Lithium Hydroxide Anhydrous
data.description: P.A.T Lithium Hydroxide Anhydrous is a chemical marvel identified by its precise chemical name, Lithium Hydroxide Anhydrous, and denoted by the CAS Number 1310-65-2. Commonly referred to as LiOH, P.A.T Lithium Hydroxide Anhydrous is distinguished by its versatility and applicability across various industrial processes, showcasing its significance as a fundamental component in the realm of chemical synthesis and manufacturing.

data.name: Lithium Hydroxide Monohydrate
data.description: P.A.T Lithium Hydroxide Monohydrate is identified by its chemical name Lithium Hydroxide, Monohydrate, and distinguished by the CAS Number 1310-66-3. This compound caters specifically to industrial markets. P.A.T Lithium Hydroxide Monohydrate exemplifies its significance as an essential component in diverse industrial processes, showcasing its efficacy and reliability in meeting the stringent requirements of the industrial sector.

data.name: N-Octyl-Pyrrolidone Wetting Agent & Surface Active Solvent
data.description: P.A.T N-Octyl-Pyrrolidone Wetting Agent & Surface Active Solvent is a specialty surfactant which is a linear, N-alkyl-2-pyrrolidone. It combines the hydrophillic, dipolar pyrrolidone ring with a hydrophobic alkyl group and exhibits a unique combination of solvency and surface activity. NOP is multifunctional and provides a variety of performance benefits in a range of applications

data.name: Photoinitiator TPO
data.description: P.A.T Photoinitiator TPO is a phosphine oxide photoinitiator designed for UV-curable inks, coatings, and adhesives. It appears as a light yellow powder. This compound plays a crucial role in initiating the UV curing process, facilitating the rapid curing of the mentioned materials when exposed to ultraviolet light. The light yellow powder form makes it convenient for incorporation into various formulations where UV curing is desired.

data.name: ProChem PTSC
data.description: P.A.T ProChem PTSC is a chemical marvel known by its chemical name p-Toluenesulfonyl Chloride, distinguished by the CAS Number 98-59-9, and boasting a purity level of 99.0%. This compound caters specifically to industrial markets. P.A.T ProChem PTSC exemplifies excellence with its high purity, positioning itself as a crucial component in various industrial processes. With its precise chemical composition, this product meets the stringent standards of industrial applications, offering reliability and performance across a spectrum of industrial settings.

data.name: Shellac Lemon #1 Flaked Shellac
data.description: P.A.T Shellac Lemon #1 Flaked Shellac is a resin produced by the female lac bug on trees in the forests of India and Thailand. Lemon #1 shellac specifically contains between 2% and 5% natural shellac wax. When utilized, it produces milky dispersions with a medium color shade in various solvents. Coatings and films made with wax-containing shellacs result in surfaces that exhibit a satin gloss. This specific formulation offers a unique combination of resin and wax properties, making it suitable for applications where a particular color shade and satin gloss finish are desired.

data.name: Sodium Benzotriazole
data.description: P.A.T Sodium Benzotriazole comprises a 34.3% active solution of methyl 1H-benzotriazole, presenting as a colorless-to-gold liquid. Widely used in various applications within industrial markets, its distinct appearance aids easy identification within formulations in chemical manufacturing.

data.name: Succinic Acid
data.description: P.A.T Succinic Acid is a product known for its low heavy metal content, making it suitable for use in food, pharmaceuticals, and industrial applications. It appears in the form of white crystals, which is a characteristic physical attribute of this versatile acid. Its purity and low heavy metal content make it a reliable choice for a range of applications across different industries.

data.name: Sucrose Benzoate
data.description: P.A.T Sucrose Benzoate is a product recognized for its excellent UV stability, clarity, lack of color, and low solution viscosity. It yields films with outstanding depth or fullness of gloss and demonstrates a broad range of compatibility with numerous resin systems. This compound is thermally stable and resistant to hydrolysis under weakly acidic or alkaline conditions. Notably, sucrose benzoate holds FDA approval as a component in food packaging adhesives.

data.name: Sulfamic Acid

summary.name: Synonyms
items: Amidosulfonic Acid, Amidosulfuric Acid, Aminosulfonic Acid, Imidosulfonic acid, Sulfamic Acid, Sulfamidic Acid, Sulfaminic Acid

data.description: P.A.T Sulfamic Acid is presented as a white crystalline powder, primarily targeted at industrial markets and applied in chemical manufacturing processes.

data.name: Titanium Dioxide Rutile NR960
data.description: P.A.T Titanium Dioxide Rutile NR960 serves as a general-purpose rutile titanium dioxide pigment produced through the sulfate process. It finds utility in both water- and solvent-based paints. This pigment undergoes hydrophilic and lipophilic organic treatments, endowing it with excellent pigment performance.

data.name: Trityl Chloride
data.description: P.A.T Trityl Chloride refers to a triphenylmethanyl compound where three phenyl rings are bonded to a single carbon. This efficient tritylation and detritylation agent finds application as an intermediate in the production of pharmaceuticals, dyes, and various industrial chemical products. Its appearance is in the form of a white crystal powder.

data.name: TT 50S (Sodium Tolyltriazole 50%)
data.description: P.A.T TT 50S (Sodium Tolyltriazole 50%) is a 43% active aqueous solution of methyl 1 H-benzotriazole (tolyltriazole), functioning as a corrosion inhibitor for copper and copper alloys. TT 50S forms a barrier film on the surface of copper, precipitating copper from solution and thereby providing galvanic corrosion protection for other metals. It finds use in various applications, including circulating cooling systems such as cooling towers, air conditioning systems, and cutting and grinding fluids. Additionally, it is applicable in functional fluids, corrosion preventative coatings, and cleaners.

data.name: Zinc Oxide UV
data.description: P.A.T Zinc Oxide UV is a physical sun-blocking agent primarily functioning by reflecting, scattering, and absorbing ultraviolet light. Its broad effectiveness spans UVB and UVA rays, offering stability in sunlight. This agent provides enhanced protection from UVA rays compared to titanium oxide or other sunscreen chemicals, making it a reliable choice for sun protection formulations.

data.name: Zirconium Acetate (Solution)
data.description: P.A.T Zirconium Acetate (Solution) is a drying stimulator used in chemical manufacturing processes. This light yellow liquid serves as a facilitator in promoting drying actions within various chemical manufacturing applications.
